## ğŸ“Œ Usage

This project is meant to be used as:

- A personal CV / Resume
- A HTML practice project
- A college assignment
- A base template you can customize

## How to Customize

- Edit personal details in the <header>
- Update experience in the Professional Experience section
- Modify skills and ratings
- Replace email, phone, and LinkedIn with your own
- Everything is clearly structured and readable.

